{"tid":1930930,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"日本又有新藥醫武漢肺炎","createTime":"2020-03-18T01:40:09.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-18T07:00:11.000Z","uid":30791,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"59fcd0d5f4841fb0f46d67043f33d93eeb963ce0","tid":1930930,"uid":30791,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-18T01:40:09.000Z","msg":"CORONAVIRUS<br />\nChina says Japan-developed flu drug works against coronavirus<br />\nFujifilm group member's Avigan to be recommended for treatment<br />\n<br />\nSHIN WATANABE, Nikkei staff writer<br />\nMARCH 18, 2020 07:50 JST<br />\n UPDATED ON MARCH 18, 2020 10:28 JST<br />\n<br />\nThe Chinese government has been conducting clinical research on a treatment for COVID-19.   &copy; AP<br />\nDALIAN, China -- An influenza medicine developed by a Fujifilm Holdings group member is effective against the novel coronavirus, the Chinese government said Tuesday.<br />\n<br />\nThe government plans to officially recommend the drug's use for treatment. Fujifilm Toyoma Chemical developed favipiravir, sold under the brand Avigan.<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://asia.nikkei.com/Spotlight/Coronavirus/China-says-Japan-developed-flu-drug-works-against-coronavirus\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fasia.nikkei.com%2FSpotlight%2FCoronavirus%2FChina-says-Japan-developed-flu-drug-works-against-coronavirus&d=Ih%2BYJd3WmO0qFhbj2imzB426uSpwD1fkwqqc2qDkc5E%3D&h=32295ed5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://asia.nikkei.com/Spotlight/Coronavirus/China-says-Japan-developed-flu-drug-works-against-coronavirus</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://en.m.wikipedia.org/wiki/Favipiravir\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fen.m.wikipedia.org%2Fwiki%2FFavipiravir&d=Ih%2BYJd3WmO0qFhbj2imzB426uSpwD1fkwqqc2qDkc5E%3D&h=a3d6bf09\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://en.m.wikipedia.org/wiki/Favipiravir</a>"},{"pid":"53f72a5b4e439ebb1c52cd7862053757fea84760","tid":1930930,"uid":30791,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-18T01:42:05.000Z","msg":"Favipiravir is also active against influenza viruses, West Nile virus, yellow fever virus, foot-and-mouth disease virus as well as other flaviviruses, arenaviruses, bunyaviruses and alphaviruses.[3]<br />\n<br />\n好似好打得"},{"pid":"0879402809f408f029482d1ad8f0c3ee44c44461","tid":1930930,"uid":30791,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-18T03:08:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/solution.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cb2168f53d7a6014afc02d851a0d98af3daab506","tid":1930930,"uid":113277,"like":0,"dislike":7,"score":-7,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-03-18T03:12:02.000Z","msg":"富士唔係出相機，仲識整藥？？"},{"pid":"24db7de9a23b5d0abd217577b273820ffcb76754","tid":1930930,"uid":256246,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-18T03:12:57.000Z","msg":"bj<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c27e3579953725a91ae5f9dc7e7ae7ad01b4a40f","tid":1930930,"uid":53003,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-03-18T03:28:26.000Z","msg":"支国唔係好勁咩？仲未有藥出<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2ba738f82e588c1a1e2b5e21c5d6f5002c76674c","tid":1930930,"uid":79563,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"c27e3579953725a91ae5f9dc7e7ae7ad01b4a40f","tid":1930930,"uid":53003,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-03-18T03:28:26.000Z","msg":"支国唔係好勁咩？仲未有藥出<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-18T05:50:33.000Z","msg":"出咗啦<br />\n<br />\n草藥雙黃蓮呀！ <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1c64a2d9c0d29642c7070e6e4f514b18aec4353a","tid":1930930,"uid":49853,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"c27e3579953725a91ae5f9dc7e7ae7ad01b4a40f","tid":1930930,"uid":53003,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-03-18T03:28:26.000Z","msg":"支国唔係好勁咩？仲未有藥出<img src=\"/assets/